Compute time derivatives dzc,k,n / dt and dze,n / dt, using latent variable space time samples and form a dataset:
Z T r = { ( z e , n ( t ) , z c , k , n ( t ) , u k , n ( t ) , d z e , n /   d t , d z c , k , n /   d t )  |  k = 1 , ⋯ , K , n = 1 , ⋯ , N , t = 1 , ⋯ , T }
identify the parameter matrices A, B, C, G involved in the latent variable space state equations using Least Squares Estimate. The details about the Least Squares Estimate computation are given in Appendix B in S1 Text.
